OL,3,C'Scary' Derby crash leaves some
OL,4,Cstudents fearing life could change
OL,5,Cforever
OL,7,FA community is still reeling after
OL,8,Fseven people were struck by a car in
OL,9,Fthe city centre, with a worker saying
OL,10,Fit is "scary knowing your life could
OL,11,Fchange forever".
OL,13,FTheir comments come as businesses
OL,14,Freport a sharp drop in footfall and
OL,15,Fpolice step up patrols to reassure the
OL,16,Fpublic, a week after seven people were
OL,17,Fhospitalised after being struck by a
OL,18,Fcar in Derby around 9.30pm on Saturday
OL,19,F28 March.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
