CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775653862
OL,3,C'Scary' Derby crash leaves some
OL,4,Cstudents fearing life could change
OL,5,Cforever
OL,7,FDharma Mundell, who works at a
OL,8,Fnewsagents on the street, told ITV
OL,9,FNews Central Correspondent Phil
OL,10,FBrewster a lot of her friends decided
OL,11,Fto give the area a miss.
OL,13,FShe said: "It's been considerably
OL,14,Fquieter since the incident and it's
OL,15,Faffected businesses for sure.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775653862
OL,3,C'Scary' Derby crash leaves some
OL,4,Cstudents fearing life could change
OL,5,Cforever
OL,7,F"I'm a student so I know quite a lot
OL,8,Fof the students are not wanting to
OL,9,Fcome out now because it's scary
OL,10,Fknowing that your life could change
OL,11,Fforever or potentially lose your life
OL,12,Fjust from somebody outside driving."
OL,14,FShe adds that there was more police
OL,15,Fand "it's nice to know they're
OL,16,Favailable and about", before adding
OL,17,Fthat the road blocks "are slowing down
OL,18,Ftraffic but people are going around it
OL,19,Fand I'm not sure if it's going to help
OL,20,Fin the long run."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775653862
OL,3,C'Scary' Derby crash leaves some
OL,4,Cstudents fearing life could change
OL,5,Cforever
OL,7,FMeanwhile Christian Ferro, who's a
OL,8,Fstudent at the University of Derby,
OL,9,Fand was among those who helped the
OL,10,Finjured using his First Aid training
OL,11,Ffrom his sports course.
OL,13,FHe said: "I saw a lady lying on the
OL,14,Ffloor and I just held her head and
OL,15,Fmade sure she was aware while I waited
OL,16,Ffor a paramedic."
OL,18,FTo reassure locals, traffic calming
OL,19,Fmeasures were put in place by police
OL,20,Fon Friar Gate.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
