PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775653862
OL,3,C'Scary' Derby crash leaves some
OL,4,Cstudents fearing life could change
OL,5,Cforever
OL,7,FSandhu Ponnachan, 36, of Chariot
OL,8,FClose, Alvaston, appeared at Southern
OL,9,FDerbyshire Magistrates' Court on
OL,10,FWednesday 1 April, accused of
OL,11,Fdangerous driving.
OL,13,FPonnachan, who is originally from
OL,14,FIndia but now lives in Derby, was
OL,15,Farrested seven minutes after the
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775653862
OL,3,C'Scary' Derby crash leaves some
OL,4,Cstudents fearing life could change
OL,5,Cforever
OL,7,FHe was also charged with six counts of
OL,8,Fcausing grievous bodily harm with
OL,9,Fintent, one count of attempted
OL,10,Fgrievous bodily harm, and one count of
OL,11,Fpossession of a bladed article.
OL,13,FSeven people were injured, some
OL,14,Fseriously, outside the Bishop Blaise
OL,15,Fpub in Friar Gate at around 9.30pm on
OL,16,FSaturday when a black Suzuki Swift
OL,17,Fmounted the pavement.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775653862
OL,3,C'Scary' Derby crash leaves some
OL,4,Cstudents fearing life could change
OL,5,Cforever
OL,7,FThe victims were four men and three
OL,8,Fwomen aged between 36 and 52, and four
OL,9,Fhave been discharged from hospital,
OL,10,FDerbyshire Police said.
OL,12,FAppearing in the dock at the
OL,13,FMagistrates' court, Ponnachan showed
OL,14,Fno emotion.
OL,16,FHe was wearing glasses and dressed in
OL,17,Fa plain grey T-shirt, grey jogging
OL,18,Fbottom and light blue croc-type
OL,19,Ffootwear, spoke only to confirm his
OL,20,Fpersonal details, including his
OL,21,Faddress.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775653862
OL,3,C'Scary' Derby crash leaves some
OL,4,Cstudents fearing life could change
OL,5,Cforever
OL,7,FThe 36-year-old was remanded in
OL,8,Fcustody until an appearance at Derby
OL,9,FCrown Court on April 29th.
OL,11,FSpeaking after the charge, Derbyshire
OL,12,FPolice Chief Superintendent Emma
OL,13,FAldred said: "This incident has,
OL,14,Fnaturally, sent shockwaves through the
OL,15,Fcommunity of Derby and the county as a
OL,16,Fwhole."
OL,18,FShe added: "My thoughts, and those of
OL,19,Fthe wider force, remain with each of
OL,20,Fthe seven injured people, their
OL,21,Ffamilies, and witnesses at the scene."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
